name: Link Aggregation Group ID
title: LAG-ID
definition: Identifies the provider assigned circuit ID for a Link Aggregation Group.

validEntry.description: COMMON LANGUAGE Special Service Circuit Codes (CLCI S/S

validEntryNotes: This format is defined in ANSI T1.266 (ATIS- 0326600.2005), Structure for the Identification of Telecommunications Circuits for the North American Telecommunications System.
usageNotes: Required when the LAG field on the ASR Form is “N”, otherwise optional.
